data.value:
StealthBot was started in late 2009 by stealthy as a project with which to develop his C# and other programming skills. Since then, thanks to a growing and supportive userbase, it has grown to be the excellent botting solution it is today. It is stealthy's goal to continously improve StealthBot and make it the best bot solution available, not just one of the best. It is thanks to the support of you, the user, that this is possible.
Any users needing help or support are encouraged to either post on the StealthSoftware forums or join and chat in IRC. The preferred method of communication is over IRC.
